              <span id="reviewTextContainer2458155020" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11276191874633421822">Once again Julianne MacLean has created a story that will stay with you long after you have finished the book. It is a tale of betrayal, love, soul-searching, and forgiveness. There are twists and turns around every corner and through it all you will find yourself rooting for Abbie MacIntyre, a wife, mother, a woman betrayed, and truly likable protagonist.</span>

          </span>
